      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The exterior is clean with only minor rock chips and light surface scratches consistent with careful use, while the interior remains in great shape with no tears or major stains. Mechanically, it runs smoothly and has a documented service history, making it a dependable choice for its next owner. You can expect a solid, reliable driving experience with no immediate repairs needed.",
