    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is recommended only for those prepared for a significant restoration project or in need of a parts car. The engine currently has major issues and does not run reliably, requiring a complete mechanical inspection and likely an overhaul. Cosmetically, the body shows heavy rust, several deep scratches, and noticeable dents, while the interior upholstery is torn and the electronics are largely non-functional. It will need to be towed upon purchase.",
